{ This is the most common move.  11.Bf4  Nd4  12.Ne4  b6  will transpose to the line 11.Ne4 b6 12.Bf4 Nd4. }
11... b6
{ At this point I am considering  12.c3  ,  12.b3  ,  12.Bf4  and  12.a4  . These represent the four major strategies for White when castling kingside. }
