{ Or  12.exf6  exf6  13.O-O-O  f5  ,  liberating the g7-bishop, with good play. }
12... fxe5 13. Bg3 Be6
{ Black has several satisfactory moves:  13...Qa5  ,  13...Be6  and even  13...c4  , in all cases with good piece play. }
*

