10. Bg5 Be7 { Let's keep things simple and develop the kingside. } 11. Bxe7
Qxe7 12. Qd2 O-O
{ Black's development has been straightforward. There is still pressure on the d4-pawn which makes it difficult for White to undertake anything too active. Pushing the knight away with g4 will create serious holes on the kingside. Chances are balanced. }
