12. exf6 Bxf6 13. O-O O-O 14. Be3 { The isolated d-pawn needs defending. }
14... Nf5 15. Bg4 Nxe3 16. fxe3
{ After the exchange, the bishop on f6 has no opponent and therefore Black is very comfortably placed. }
16... b6
